        "text_hU6C6L": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2>The Aetrex Difference</h2><p>What makes our shoes different, and what makes our shoes better, is all tied to our technology and our knowledge of feet.<br/><br/>When a shoe is made, it’s built over something called a last, which determines its 3-dimensional shape. At Aetrex, we have millions of 3D scans in our database. And, these scans help us develop our unique lasts. We’re able to create shoes that fit better, because it’s all tied to scientific data. We don’t have to guess.<br/></p>",
            "text_font": "body",
            "text_size": "subtext-md",
