        "text_aNzLAw": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Our scans also tell us where your pressure points are located when you walk or run. So, our footbeds and removable insoles are designed specifically to offload impact at these areas of high pressure.</p><p>And every shoe in our collection features Aetrex’s Signature Arch Support. It’s designed to help create proper alignment throughout your gait cycle. By doing this, we can reduce pronation, which helps prevent injuries and promotes proper foot health.</p>",
